title: Unmistakeably one of the most money saving apartments in Austin
posting_body: Recently renovated studio apartment designed for Austinites looking for just a tiny, peaceful haven to settle into while staying connected to the very best of Austin.
With designer finishes, new appliances, and a renovated pool, you'll love lounging, cooking, and entertaining at this apartment complex on North Lamar.
Austin at its best with plenty of excellent restaurants, shopping, and entertainment nearby.
Central and downtown Austin are just minutes away, and lush outdoors can be found just north at the Walnut Creek Greenbelt.
So come discover for yourself—you're going to love what you find & the money you save.
Will accept all misdemeanors, except for violence, no matter how recent.
Christena Barry - Award Winning Locator & Realtor
*Pics show general property, not necessarily particular unit.
